            <title>[FLINK-1296] Add support for very large record for sorting</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-1296</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently, very large records (multiple hundreds of megabytes) can break the sorter if the overflow the sort buffer.&lt;/p&gt;

